---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import ToolCard from "../components/ToolCard.astro";
import { SITE } from "../config/site";
---

<BaseLayout title={SITE.title} description={SITE.description} canonicalPath="/">
	<section
		class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm md:p-10"
	>
		<p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-teal-700">
			SEO + Fast Utilities
		</p>
		<h1
			class="mt-4 text-4xl font-black leading-tight text-slate-900 md:text-5xl"
		>
			Developer Tools Cepat, Ringan, dan Bisa Diindeks Google
		</h1>
		<p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
			Koleksi utility paling sering dipakai developer: JSON formatter,
			regex tester, JWT decoder, timestamp converter, UUID generator,
			base64, URL encode/decode, dan HTML encode/decode. Semua halaman
			dioptimalkan untuk load cepat dan mudah diindeks mesin pencari.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3">
		<ToolCard
			title="JSON Formatter / Validator"
			description="Validasi, beautify, dan minify JSON untuk debugging API request/response."
			href="/tools/json-formatter-validator"
			status="Popular"
		/>
		<ToolCard
			title="JSON Viewer Suite"
			description="Parse JSON, unstringify JSON string, beautify output, convert to XML/CSV dalam satu halaman."
			href="/tools/json-viewer"
			status="Priority"
		/>
		<ToolCard
			title="Regex Tester"
			description="Uji pola regular expression lengkap dengan flags dan daftar hasil match."
			href="/tools/regex-tester"
		/>
		<ToolCard
			title="JWT Decoder"
			description="Decode JWT header dan payload untuk debugging autentikasi token."
			href="/tools/jwt-decoder"
		/>
		<ToolCard
			title="Timestamp Converter"
			description="Konversi Unix timestamp ke tanggal normal dan sebaliknya."
			href="/tools/timestamp-converter"
		/>
		<ToolCard
			title="UUID Generator"
			description="Generate UUID v4 cepat untuk kebutuhan ID unik aplikasi."
			href="/tools/uuid-generator"
		/>
		<ToolCard
			title="HTML Encode / Decode"
			description="Encode/decode HTML entities untuk output aman di frontend/CMS."
			href="/tools/html-encode-decode"
		/>
		<ToolCard
			title="Base64 Encode / Decode"
			description="Encode text ke Base64 dan decode kembali dengan cepat langsung di browser."
			href="/tools/base64-encode-decode"
		/>
		<ToolCard
			title="URL Encode / Decode"
			description="Encode karakter spesial untuk query/path URL dan decode kembali ke teks normal."
			href="/tools/url-encode-decode"
		/>
		<ToolCard
			title="Base64 to Image"
			description="Render Base64 image (PNG/JPG/WEBP), preview, dan download hasil gambar."
			href="/tools/base64-to-image"
		/>
		<ToolCard
			title="AES Encrypt / Decrypt"
			description="Enkripsi-dekripsi dua arah (bukan hash) dengan AES-GCM langsung di browser."
			href="/tools/aes-encrypt-decrypt"
		/>
		<ToolCard
			title="Hash Generator"
			description="Generate hash one-way: MD5, SHA-1, SHA-256, SHA-384, SHA-512, plus info Tiger dan bcrypt."
			href="/tools/hash-generator"
		/>
	</section>

	<section
		class="mt-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm md:p-8"
	>
		<h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900">
			Tools Populer untuk Workflow Harian
		</h2>
		<p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
			JSON formatter, regex tester, dan JWT decoder adalah kombinasi
			paling sering dipakai saat debugging API. Timestamp converter dan
			UUID generator membantu operasi backend sehari-hari, sedangkan
			URL/HTML encode-decode berguna untuk query string, rendering, dan
			sanitasi.
		</p>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
